"Create a new directory in your project for ``Lab 04 - Camel`` and a file "
"called ``lab_04.py`` in that folder if the folder and file don't exist "
"already."
msgstr ""
"Erstelle ein neues Verzeichnis in deinem Projekt für ``Lab 04 - Camel`` "
